$$x = \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} \mathbf{c}^T \mathbf{x}$$  
thoả mãn:  $\mathbf{A}\mathbf{x} = \mathbf{b}$  (25.9)
$\mathbf{x} \succeq 0$
